WEBVTT

00:02:59.225 --> 00:03:00.493
katika tafiti,

00:03:00.517 --> 00:03:04.294
alikuwa ni mama mjane anayefanya biashara,

00:03:04.318 --> 00:03:05.806
akilea watoto wake.

00:03:07.092 --> 00:03:09.702
Ni kipi kilibadili udhanifu wetu?

00:03:09.726 --> 00:03:11.245
Kipi kilitushangaza?

00:03:11.269 --> 00:03:14.991
Kwanza, Teresia analipia kodi ya serikali ya soko la mkoa

00:03:15.015 --> 00:03:16.846
kila siku anayofanya biashara

00:03:16.870 --> 00:03:20.123
kutokana na kuweka biashara chini ya mti wake.

00:03:20.147 --> 00:03:22.198
Amekuwa akifanya hivi kwa miaka saba,

00:03:22.222 --> 00:03:24.144
na amekuwa akipewa risiti.

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:26.037
Anatunza kumbumkumbu.

00:03:26.061 --> 00:03:29.228
Tunamuona asiye hafifu,

00:03:29.252 --> 00:03:30.599
masikini,